Celez...

543
00:27:22,110 --> 00:27:24,490
你符合一项实验治疗的标准
you meet the criteria for an experimental treatment

544
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:27,400
我认为这能让你免受植皮手术之苦
that I think will prevent you from having to undergo skin grafts.

545
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:29,620
慢着  怎么会有这样的事
Hold up. How did this even happen?

546
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,560
我发现圣地亚哥的试验
Well, I found out San Diego's trial

547
00:27:31,560 --> 00:27:33,610
允许多站点协作
allows for multi-site collaborations.

548
00:27:33,610 --> 00:27:35,650
所以我们不用有自己的伦理委员会
So, there's no need for us to get our own I.R.B.

549
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:38,950
他们把皮给我们  我们提供病人数据
They give us the skins, we provide the patient data.

550
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:40,250
鱼皮吗
Fish skins?

551
00:27:40,670 --> 00:27:43,720
罗非鱼皮已经被清洗和杀菌
The tilapia skins have been cleaned and sterilized.

552
00:27:43,740 --> 00:27:44,990
