572
00:28:44,930 --> 00:28:47,040
不  我们已经知道答案了  他们不知道
No, we already know the answer. They don't know.

573
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:48,550
以前从未做过这种手术
This thing has never been done before.

574
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:49,610
安静
Be quiet!

575
00:28:57,810 --> 00:29:00,430
他的脚趾在变色
His toes are changing color.

576
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:03,380
动脉

577
00:29:02,710 --> 00:29:04,030
受损

578
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:06,200
导致凝血

579
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:11,580
他在凝血  糟了  马上呼叫梅伦德斯医生
He's clotting. That's bad. Page Dr. Melendez stat!

580
00:29:15,370 --> 00:29:17,500
-莫菲  什么情况  -血液分流在凝血
- Murphy, what do we got? - The shunt is clotting.

581
00:29:17,500 --> 00:29:19,580
它在限制血流  它不行了
It's restricting blood flow. It is failing.

582
00:29:19,630 --> 00:29:20,990
好吧  我们现在要做个决定
All right, we need a decision now.

583
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:22,660
要截腿还是换骨
Are we cutting off the leg or replacing the bone?

584
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:24,470
我相信马尔科的父母和未婚妻
There's no doubt in my mind that Marco's parents

585
00:29:24,470 --> 00:29:27,340
都很爱他  但现在显然...
and fiancée all love Marco, but it's become clear --

586
00:29:27,340 --> 00:29:29,100
现在给我个决定
Now. I need a decision now.

587
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,210
在父母眼中他是孩子
His parents know him as their child.

588
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:34,840
但在索尼娅心中他是成年人
Sonia knows him as a man.

589
00:29:35,690 --> 00:29:36,930
换股骨
Replace the femur.

590
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,130
走吧
Let's go!

591
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:43,050
谢谢  谢谢
Thank you! Thank you.

592
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:54,300
-那就是出血  看见了吗  -看见了
- And there's the bleed. See it? - Yes, sir.

593
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:56,980
你有夹过颅内动脉吗
You ever clip an intracranial artery before?

594
00:29:57,890 --> 00:29:58,740
没有
No, sir.

595
00:29:59,410 --> 00:30:00,340
来吧
Go for it.

596
00:30:08,130 --> 00:30:09,860
每个第一次都一样
Just like every first time --

597
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:13,660
你有点激动  有点恶心
you're a little excited, a little nauseous.

598
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,290
希望没人受伤
Hopefully nobody gets hurt.

599
00:30:35,150 --> 00:30:36,200
准备好了吗
Is it good to go?

600
00:30:37,120 --> 00:30:38,640
非常好
It's very good.

601
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:39,610
钳子
Forceps.

602
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:45,900
你准备好了吗
You ready?

603
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:47,840
是的
Yes.

604
00:31:19,910 --> 00:31:24,320
确保夹子的利片不会碰到有孔动脉
Be careful the clip blades don't catch any perforated arteries.

605
00:31:25,270 --> 00:31:27,320
我没看见有血管挡着
I don't seen any vessels in the way.

606
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:28,640
那你还在等什么
Then what are you waiting for?

607
00:31:34,390 --> 00:31:35,390
非常好
Very nice.

608
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,330
谢谢
Thank you.

609
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:42,020
没有出血
Everything's dry.

610
00:31:42,020 --> 00:31:43,600
道别完就盖上去吧
Say goodbye and close the roof.

611
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:48,060
我们得在一分钟左右
We need to get blood back into his leg

612
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:49,580
让血流回他的腿
in the next minute or so,

613
00:31:50,130 --> 00:31:51,980
否则我还是得做截肢
or I'm gonna have to amputate after all.

614
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:54,800
吊了胰岛素  给他输钙
Insulin's hanging, loaded him with calcium.

615
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:55,910
尽我所能
Best I can do.

616
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:57,320
现在拿掉钳夹
Let's release the clamps.

617
00:31:59,970 --> 00:32:01,380
检查毛细管充血
Check for capillary refill.

618
00:32:14,610 --> 00:32:16,070
血流已修复
Blood flow is restored.

619
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:19,380
心电图正常
EKG is normal.

620
00:32:21,870 --> 00:32:26,470
金  我要听到类似「变化」和「增量」的词
Okay. Kim, I want to hear words like "Variability" and "Delta".

621
00:32:26,510 --> 00:32:27,540
说给我听
Give them to me.

622
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,570
我在耐心等待
I'm waiting patiently.

623
00:32:33,090 --> 00:32:34,390
什么也没有
I'm not getting anything.

624
00:32:35,650 --> 00:32:36,500
给我看看
Show me.

625
00:32:44,820 --> 00:32:45,830
检查引线
Check the leads.

626
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:54,160
还是没有
Still nothing.

627
00:32:54,900 --> 00:32:57,090
也许是神经重塑
Maybe there will be some neuroplasticity.

628
00:32:57,360 --> 00:33:00,440
她的大脑自己重新连接
Her brain -- I-it could rewire itself.

629
00:33:01,110 --> 00:33:01,800
不
No.

630
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:06,230
没有脑部活动
Zero brain activity.

631
00:33:06,230 --> 00:33:07,990
我不知道为什么  但她去世了
I don't know why, but she's gone.

632
00:33:26,560 --> 00:33:27,300
什么
What?

633
00:33:27,450 --> 00:33:29,520
你的神经外科病人今晚死了
Your neurosurgery patient that died tonight --

634
00:33:29,610 --> 00:33:31,090
有件事你该知道
there's something you should know.

635
00:33:31,570 --> 00:33:32,350
什么
What?

636
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:42,560
马尔科  我要你尝试动动你的脚趾
Now, Marco, I want you to try and move your toes.

637
00:33:54,260 --> 00:33:55,250
我不能
I can't.

638
00:33:55,630 --> 00:33:56,480
他还好吗
Is he okay?

639
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:57,450
我们不确定骨...
We're not sure if the bone --

640
00:33:57,450 --> 00:33:58,350
他不会死吧
He's not gonna die?

641
00:33:58,350 --> 00:34:00,060
他不会被感染吧
H-He's not gonna get an infection?

642
00:34:00,060 --> 00:34:00,860
-他的身体不会排斥... -不
- His body's not gonna reject -- - No, no.

643
00:34:00,860 --> 00:34:02,740
我们密切监控他
We're monitoring him very closely.

644
00:34:02,740 --> 00:34:04,540
-最大的威胁... -他动了
- The biggest threat is behind -- - He moved.

645
00:34:05,370 --> 00:34:06,440
他动了
He moved.

646
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:14,750
成功了
It worked.

647
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,670
有漫长的复原期等着你
You'll have a long recovery ahead --

648
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:19,420
好几个月的物理治疗
months of physical therapy.

649
00:34:19,720 --> 00:34:21,140
不过现在  你应该好好休息
But for now, all you have to do is rest.

650
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:22,150
谢谢你
Thank you.

651
00:34:22,850 --> 00:34:26,520
感谢你救了我的命  挽救了我的腿
Thank you for saving my life -- for saving my leg.

652
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:29,450
-谢谢  -不用谢
- Thank you. - You're welcome, sir.

653
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:36,580
准备好接着办完我们的事了吗
Are you ready to finish what we started?

654
00:34:38,620 --> 00:34:40,080
先好起来再说
Get well first.

655
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:43,230
有的是时间办婚礼
There's plenty of time for a wedding.

656
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:53,310
-谢谢  -不用谢
- Thank you. - You're welcome, sir.

657
00:34:53,740 --> 00:34:54,560
谢谢
Thank you.

658
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:03,560
你看起来很好
You look good.

659
00:35:03,670 --> 00:35:05,910
坚强  就像潜水侠
Tough. Like Aquaman.

660
00:35:10,470 --> 00:35:11,980
我看起来像寿司
I look like sushi.

661
00:35:12,220 --> 00:35:13,850
大家都爱吃寿司
Everybody loves sushi.

662
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:16,900
只需要六个月
It's only for six months.

663
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:19,110
你的新皮肤应该就能完全长好了
Your new skin should have completely grown in by then.

664
00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:20,570
瘢痕应该会很小
Should have minor scarring.

665
00:35:22,020 --> 00:35:23,240
谢谢
Thank you.

666
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:26,970
我误会你了
I misjudged you.

667
00:35:29,270 --> 00:35:30,590
你对我的评判很准确
You judged me just right.

668
00:35:43,210 --> 00:35:44,380
她还在睡吗
Is she still sleeping?

669
00:35:45,720 --> 00:35:47,520
-你还没告诉她吗  -没有
- You haven't told her yet? - No.

670
00:35:49,330 --> 00:35:50,850
能出来一下吗
Can I have a moment please?

671
00:35:51,810 --> 00:35:52,660
当然
Of course.

672
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:03,110
你在事故现场发现珍娜后多久
How soon after you found Jenna at the crash site

673
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:04,780
给她插的管
did you intubate her?

674
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,140
几乎是立刻就插了
Almost immediately.

675
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,320
我按压她的胸骨
I did a sternal rub.

676
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:10,060
她表现出去大脑强直
She had decerebrate posturing.

677
00:36:10,060 --> 00:36:11,750
她的左侧瞳孔已经散大
Her left pupil was blown.

678
00:36:11,820 --> 00:36:13,380
我知道她出现了硬膜下血肿
I knew she had a subdural hematoma,

679
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:16,040
所以我插了管  钻了孔
so I intubated, did the burr hole.

680
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:18,820
并且她还有连枷胸
She also had a flail chest.

681
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,670
你插管之后检查她的呼吸了吗
Did you check her breathing after you intubated her?

682
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,410
查了
Yes.

683
00:36:24,890 --> 00:36:27,750
我觉得我应该查了
Well, at least I-I think I did.

684
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:33,950
利姆医生说珍娜到急诊的时候
Dr. Lim told me that when Jenna came into the E.R.,

685
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,890
她的呼吸并不正常
she wasn't ventilating properly.

686
00:36:35,890 --> 00:36:37,830
你插管插得太深了
You inserted the tube too deep

687
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:40,600
插进了她伤侧肺的
into her right main stem bronchus

688
00:36:40,850 --> 00:36:42,770
右主支气管
of her injured lung.

689
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:44,640
我们没法估计
We had no way of knowing

690
00:36:45,140 --> 00:36:49,030
在做脑电图前她已经缺氧了多久
how long she was hypoxic before we gave her the EEG.

691
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:03,570
我在她颅骨上钻了一个非常完美的孔
I drilled a perfect burr hole into her skull

692
00:37:03,570 --> 00:37:04,950
还是在夜里  在马路边
on the side of the road in the middle of the night,

693
00:37:04,950 --> 00:37:07,770
但我  我插管却插坏了
and I-I-I screw up her intubation?

694
00:37:08,490 --> 00:37:09,010
是的
Yes.

695
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:11,280
即使是高年资医生  当时的情况
It was tough conditions for anyone --

696
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,490
也是非常棘手的
resident or not.

697
00:37:12,660 --> 00:37:14,980
我们任何人都有可能犯同样的错误
Any one of us could have made the same mistake.

698
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:32,900
我曾经在急诊室接诊过一个女病人
I had a woman come into the E.R. once...

699
00:37:34,230 --> 00:37:36,650
51岁  是个母亲
a mother, 51 years old.

700
00:37:37,670 --> 00:37:39,530
弗朗辛·帕克
Francine Parker.

701
00:37:40,210 --> 00:37:41,560
她有两个儿子
She had two boys.

702
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:44,020
她因为咳嗽来的
She had a cough --

703
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:47,580
很剧烈  但也不过是个咳嗽
a bad one -- but a cough.

704
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,650
我给她做了检查
I checked her out,

705
00:37:49,650 --> 00:37:51,520
给她开了点抗生素就让她回去了
gave her some antibiotics, sent her home.

706
00:37:51,720 --> 00:37:54,680
六小时后  她被人送来急诊
Six hours later, she was rolled into the E.R..

707
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:58,230
她得了心脏病  我没发现  结果
She had had a heart attack, and I missed it, and...

708
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:00,730
她死了
she died.

709
00:38:04,050 --> 00:38:06,430
从那时起
Not one day...

710
00:38:06,770 --> 00:38:09,190
之后我的每一天我都会想起她
goes by when I don't think about her.

711
00:38:11,530 --> 00:38:13,050
她是你的第一例
She was your first.

712
00:38:14,790 --> 00:38:17,180
其实  是第四例
My fourth, actually.

713
00:38:19,650 --> 00:38:21,880
你不会忘记这种病例的
You're not gonna forget this.

714
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:24,170
永远忘不了
You never forget.

715
00:38:25,050 --> 00:38:27,620
但可能  下次遇到这些病例
But I don't know, maybe we're better off for it

716
00:38:27,620 --> 00:38:28,980
我们可以做得更好
the next time around.

717
00:38:30,650 --> 00:38:32,680
你得努力振作起来
You got to find a way to keep going.

718
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,740
回家去  去睡吧
Go home. Get some rest.

719
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:42,470
我都还没有告诉她
I haven't even told her yet.

720
00:38:42,470 --> 00:38:43,840
你不准去
You're not going to.

721
00:38:45,470 --> 00:38:47,940
你犯了个错误  你与此事关系太大
You made a mistake. You're too close to this.

722
00:38:47,940 --> 00:38:50,180
我不能让你去和家属
I'm not gonna allow you to talk to the family

723
00:38:50,180 --> 00:38:54,360
或院外的任何人谈论这事
or anyone else outside this hospital about this.

724
00:38:55,890 --> 00:38:57,430
你听明白了吗
Do we understand each other?

